"""
BSS Analyzer — generates a self-contained HTML dashboard from BSSLogs CSVs.

Usage:
    python bss_analyze.py                        # auto-finds latest session
    python bss_analyze.py --session "Session 3"  # specific session
    python bss_analyze.py --all                  # merge all sessions

Output: BSS_Dashboard.html  (open in any browser)

Requirements:
    pip install pandas
"""

